instruction: Select the best photo from the following choice of four photos.
input:
(1) A portrait photo of a bird flying in front of a lake, 
(2) A photo of a sunrise over the horizon, 
(3) A photo of a city skyline, 
(4) A landscape photo of a mountain and valley.
output: The best photo from the four choices is (2) A photo of a sunrise over the horizon. It has vibrant colors, an intriguing sky, and serene beauty.
